\##

<center>✨ Project Overview ✨</center>

**Title:** Customer Satisfaction in the Airline Industry\
**Data Source:** Anonymized real airline dataset with 120,000+ passenger responses\
**Sampling:** Non-probability convenience sampling

------------------------------------------------------------------------

\##

<center>🚨 Business Problem</center>

Customer satisfaction is a crucial metric in a competitive airline market.

<aside class="notes">

This slide introduces the problem we're trying to solve. Highlight how competition is fierce and satisfaction matters.

</aside>

------------------------------------------------------------------------

\##

<center>Why It Matters</center>

-   Enhance customer service {.fragment}
-   Retain loyal passengers {.fragment}
-   Stay ahead in a competitive market {.fragment}

------------------------------------------------------------------------

\##

<center>🎯 Audience</center>

This project is designed for:

-   **Airline Management Teams** {.fragment}
-   Seeking to improve **customer experience** {.fragment}

------------------------------------------------------------------------

\##

<center>🎓 Research Objectives</center>

-   **Objective 1:** Inflight Service Quality → Satisfaction (*Kiki Shimomae*) {.fragment}
-   **Objective 2:** Operational Efficiency → Satisfaction (*Janette Limon*) {.fragment}
-   **Objective 3:** Demographics & Travel Purpose → Satisfaction (*Marvin Castrejon*) {.fragment}
-   **Objective 4:** Comfort & Accessibility → Satisfaction (*Stephanie Alcocer*) {.fragment}

------------------------------------------------------------------------

\##

<center>🚀 Expected Impact</center>

Insights from this project will help airlines:

-   🎯 Prioritize resources {.fragment}
-   💡 Refine customer service strategies {.fragment}
-   ❤️ Improve customer loyalty {.fragment}

------------------------------------------------------------------------

\##

<center>🔍 Key Insights – Objective 2</center>

**Impact of Operational Efficiency on Satisfaction**\
*Janette Limon*

------------------------------------------------------------------------

### 📉 What Hurts Satisfaction?

-   ⏱️ **Flight delays** significantly reduce satisfaction {.fragment}
-   👔 **Business travelers** tolerate short delays {.fragment}
-   ⏳ Longer disruptions? **Much less forgiving** {.fragment}

------------------------------------------------------------------------

### 💼 Opportunities for Improvement

-   ✈️ Improve **baggage handling** {.fragment}
-   🕓 Optimize **time convenience** {.fragment}
-   🎯 Focus on efficiency during peak times {.fragment}

------------------------------------------------------------------------

